text: The 2014–15 Utah State Aggies women's basketball team represents Utah State University in the 2014–15 college basketball season. The Aggies, led by third year head coach Jerry Finkbeiner. The Aggies played their home games at the Smith Spectrum and were second year members of the Mountain West Conference. They finish the season 8–23, 5–13 in Mountain West play in a tie to finish in tenth place.
